907
00:46:37,190 --> 00:46:38,490
<b>Who are they?</b>

908
00:46:44,899 --> 00:46:48,169
<b>I see. I must admit
that you're a man of loyalty.</b>

909
00:46:49,500 --> 00:46:52,639
<b>But you should think
of your current situation.</b>

910
00:46:52,970 --> 00:46:54,446
<b>You're practically a freeloader now.</b>

911
00:46:54,470 --> 00:46:56,716
