913
00:46:58,710 --> 00:47:00,625
<b>I know, but I have no choice.</b>

914
00:47:00,649 --> 00:47:02,710
<b>The mold is just killing them.</b>

915
00:47:02,750 --> 00:47:05,525
<b>Gosh, you're so helpless.</b>

916
00:47:05,549 --> 00:47:07,726
<b>I will get them a new place
